text: First of all, you need some common sense to get by in the world and it is doubly so for highly competitive spaces. All of these day trading YouTube channels with their shorts, pulling up some random ass lines saying, Oh, it's a double top. This is always a great signal. It works every time. And then you get the old order filled and then they make 10,000 in 10 minutes. Listen, if you actually think that's how this works, you deserve to fail. You've got to have some common sense in this space and that ain't it. The Anautler or C.O. later.
